## So the net changes are

### Add

* `spring-boot-starter-oauth2-resource-server`
* `JwtDecoder` bean
* `JwtService` using decoder

### Keep unchanged

* `/auth/start`
* `/auth/callback`
* token exchange code
* Redis auth transaction flow
* Lancelot-based app config flow

### Optional safety

* minimal `SecurityFilterChain` so Spring does not alter behavior

